He's disappeared.
We can't find him anywhere.

994
01:12:02,787 --> 01:12:04,345
You didn't look in the right place.

995
01:12:04,427 --> 01:12:06,861
He was to make a speech
before the curtain went up.

996
01:12:07,027 --> 01:12:09,018
[Orchestra playing cue]

997
01:12:09,107 --> 01:12:11,177
That's the cue.
You'd better say something.

998
01:12:11,267 --> 01:12:12,939
But I never made a speech in my life.

999
01:12:13,027 --> 01:12:15,495
-All right, I'll take care of it.
-You?

1000
01:12:16,387 --> 01:12:18,184
Ladies and gentlemen....

1001
