How would you like to feel
the way she looks?

1053
01:16:41,467 --> 01:16:43,458
That is Driftwood's voice.

1054
01:16:43,547 --> 01:16:46,425
-I want him put out of the opera house.
-Yes, sir.

1055
01:17:02,907 --> 01:17:05,102
That's right. You go talk to him.

1056
01:17:09,787 --> 01:17:11,266
[Singing continues]

1057
