1058
01:17:15,667 --> 01:17:18,135
-Where's Mr. Gottlieb?
-The other side of the stage.

1059
01:17:18,227 --> 01:17:19,626
Come on, boys.

1060
01:17:26,987 --> 01:17:29,660
What was that? High "C" or vitamin "D"?

1061
01:17:38,507 --> 01:17:40,259
[All singing]

1062
