-That's who I am.

1084
01:22:24,667 --> 01:22:26,100
Get into a costume quickly.

1085
01:22:26,187 --> 01:22:28,178
-What?
-I want you to sing.

1086
01:22:30,347 --> 01:22:33,066
But I have no reputation, Mr. Gottlieb.

1087
01:22:33,147 --> 01:22:36,025
Besides, I couldn't sing
with a strange Leonora.

1088
01:22:36,107 --> 01:22:38,496
