Rosa, Baroni, get out there quick.

1108
01:25:54,267 --> 01:25:56,417
No. I'm under arrest, Mr. Gottlieb.

1109
01:25:56,507 --> 01:25:59,465
-What's that?
-If they're arrested, I ought to be, too.

1110
01:25:59,547 --> 01:26:01,344
